      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is a total dream\u2014it\u2019s in pristine, mint condition and has been babied since day one. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! If you're looking for something that's been impeccably cared for and is ready for its next adventure, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
